        <briefdescription>
<para>Idle state handler function for OtaStart events. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
<para><simplesect kind="return"><para>Returns the state ID of the triggered state</para>
</simplesect>
The function notify platform that command is accepted by calling function otaStartConfirm of the <ref refid="class_fw_upd_ctrl" kindref="compound">FwUpdCtrl</ref> class instance. Pointer variable pd is assigned to <ref refid="class_fw_upd_ctrl" kindref="compound">FwUpdCtrl</ref> class instance. Function start the trigger timeout timer by calling function startTimeout of the <ref refid="class_fw_upd_ctrl" kindref="compound">FwUpdCtrl</ref> class instance. Finally function returns the state ID eTriggered. </para>
        </detaileddescription>
